        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDan this is attempt to fix all ccsdk-*-master-release-version-java-daily jobs. Example: https://jenkins.onap.org/view/ccsdk/job/ccsdk-sli-core-master-release-version-java-daily/42/console\n\nSeem there isn't an onap.nexus.staging.profile-id and if I remember correctly you might have excluded this in an attempt to skip staging. But the build is failing on trying to use this profile-id and do staging anyway. \n\nI think this will clear way for sonar, which runs after staging.",
